                  </persName>
            . I received this hat from Mr. Horlor, in the street - I had seen the prisoner running with it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310512-115-person896">
                  SAMPSON 
                  HENRY PERRY
               <interp inst="t18310512-115-person896" type="surname" value="HENRY PERRY"></interp>
